
:: InitSmithy [output]
<<set $currentPassageBuilding to ($town.buildings[$currentPassage.key] || $town.buildings[$currentPassage.key])>><<run lib.clampRolls($town.buildings[$currentPassage.key].roll)>>
<<linkreplace "Rename <strong>$currentPassageBuilding.name</strong>">><h3><<textbox "$currentPassageBuilding.name" $currentPassageBuilding.name>></h3><</linkreplace>>

<<button "Delete $currentPassageBuilding.name">><<run setup.deleteBuilding($town, $currentPassageBuilding)>><<goto "Start">><</button>>

<span class="tip" title="How wealthy is the patronage?">Smithy Wealth: <<numberslider "$currentPassageBuilding.roll.wealth" $currentPassageBuilding.roll.wealth 1 100 1>></span>

<span class="tip" title="How large is the smithy?">Smithy Size: <<numberslider "$currentPassageBuilding.roll.size" $currentPassageBuilding.roll.size 1 100 1>></span>

<span class="tip" title="Is it well known, or does the guy just shoe horses?">Smithy Reputation: <<numberslider "$currentPassageBuilding.roll.reputation" $currentPassageBuilding.roll.reputation 1 100 1>></span>

<span class="tip" title="How clean is the smithy?">Smithy Cleanliness: <<numberslider "$currentPassageBuilding.roll.cleanliness" $currentPassageBuilding.roll.cleanliness 1 100 1>></span>

<span class="tip" title="How skilled is the blacksmith?">Smithy Expertise: <<numberslider "$currentPassageBuilding.roll.expertise" $currentPassageBuilding.roll.expertise 1 100 1>></span>

<span class="tip" title="How busy is the blacksmith? Does he have a backlog a mile long, or is he sitting idle?">Smithy Activity: <<numberslider "$currentPassageBuilding.roll.activity" $currentPassageBuilding.roll.activity 1 100 1>></span>

<span class="tip" title="How do the prices here compare to your average blacksmith?">Smithy Price Modifier: <<numberslider "$currentPassageBuilding.priceModifier" $currentPassageBuilding.priceModifier -10 10 1>></span>

